A fully managed service for file transfers into and out of amazon s3 or EFS using the FTP protocol
supported protocols
  FTP (file tansfer protocol) <-- UNENCRYPTED
  FTPS (file tansfer protocol USING SSL)
  SFTP (sECUREfile tansfer protocol)
managed infrastructure, scalable, reliable, multi az
pay per provisioned endpoint per hour + data transfers in GB
Store and manage users credentials within the service
integrate with existing authentication systems
use:
  sharing files
  public datasets
  CRM
  ERP
Route 53 optional
